recipes.description: a new recipe, ripe for a plump and savory definition.

categories.name: Chef de Cuisine
categories.description:
Cooking of the finest calibur, refined to the MAX.
Admittedly, the ingredients available in these parts make for some strange dishes.

categories.name: Bar's Tender
categories.description:
One must understand that drinks can make or break the tension like a hot knife through butter.
Or through a hot rum cocktail, or even a cold glass of chocolate malk.

categories.name: Bladesmithing
categories.description:
\C[1]Bladesmithing\C[0] is an ancient and very hot trade.
Literally, because anvils and hammers and shit are required to make your one and two handers, and dual-wielders.

categories.name: Spearcrafting
categories.description:
Ye olde \C[1]Spearcrafting\C[0] is a means to bond nature's long with sharp.
Crafting clubs, spears, and javelins will enable you to hunt at any distance.

categories.name: Gungineering
categories.description:
The amazing \C[1]Gungineering\C[0] is a stupendous means of making machines for war.
Not just any machines, in fact only pistols, shotguns, and tasers.

categories.name: Axeworkery
categories.description:
\C[1]Axeworkery\C[0] is the slapdash method of creating axes.
With practice, anyone can put out some impressive one or two handers, and eventually even a twin axe.

categories.name: Wandfusion
categories.description:
Legendary \C[1]Wandfusion\C[0] is the technomancy behind the creation of wands and the like.
The wizards and wizardesses of yore used to empower staves and wands, and even books nowadays to do the deeds.

categories.name: Fistmanship
categories.description:
The art of \C[1]Fistmanship\C[0] goes back as far as 178k years ago.
To master fistmanship is to master not just the fists, but the claws and the arms.

categories.name: Sole Defender
categories.description:
The craft of the \C[1]Sole Defender\C[0] creates unparalleled defensive armaments.
Outputs ranging from magical support relics to beefy kite shields, your defenses can be saved here.

categories.name: The Weaver
categories.description:
The deliberate hand of \C[1]The Weaver\C[0] is unmatched.
Producing both delicate mystical robes and enduring steel plate mail, your defenses shall be saved here.

categories.name: Fabulous Footwork
categories.description:
A light-hearted adventurer is he who started the \C[1]Fabulous Footwork\C[0] club.
Only those most dedicated to comfort and protection of the feet dare apply here.

categories.name: Runic Creations
categories.description:
One who can create the runes can control the world- or so they say.
"Runes" are typically just enhancements for equips relating to optimizing combat potential.

categories.name: Gemology
categories.description:
The alchemy of gems is a wild science that many correlate with the Philosopher's Stone or
with turning shit into gold. How about turning shit into gems that give your stats a boost?
